headline: Here’s Appalaches Capital’s Investment Thesis For CSX Corporation (CSX)
summary: Appalaches Capital, an investment management firm, released its third-quarter 2024, investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. Appalaches Core LO ended the quarter with a 3.0% gain after all fees and expenses compared to the S&P 500’s return of 5.9%, the equal-weighted S&P 500’s return of 9.6%, and the SOFR Index […]
